verbose_text: XREF_TABLE shows that the order does not change much in this range, and that, though there is a tendency that the most anterior gene hoxa1 and hoxa2 (PGs 1 and 2) are expressed early, and that the posterior hox genes of hoxa11 and hoxa13 (PGs 11 and 13) are expressed late, the order does not match the order of central genes in the cluster (PGs 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 9 and 10).
